1
00:00:02,260 --> 00:00:07,870

2
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,430
1462年
The year, 1462.

3
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:44,670
康斯坦丁堡陷落
Constantinople had fallen.

4
00:00:45,510 --> 00:00:49,240
信奉回教的土耳其人大军横扫欧洲
Moslem Turks swept into Europe with a vast, superior force...

5
00:00:49,510 --> 00:00:53,500
痛击罗马尼亚威胁整个基督教世界
striking at Romania, threatening all of Christendom.

6
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:58,220
川索凡尼亚有一名圣龙会武士
From Transylvania arose a Romanian knight of the Sacred Order of the Dragon,

7
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,920
名叫德古拉
known as Dracula.

8
00:01:16,870 --> 00:01:19,140
战役前夕
On the eve of the battle...

9
00:01:19,270 --> 00:01:24,940
他挚爱的新娘伊丽莎白
his bride Elisabeta whom he prized above all things on Earth...

10
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:29,480
知道他将与强敌对阵
knew that he must face an insurmountable force...

11
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:33,150
可能一去不返
from which he might never return.

12
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,940
(赞美主)

13
00:02:33,010 --> 00:02:34,950
(我已获胜)

14
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,620
伊丽莎白
Elisabeta.

15
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:52,960
诡诈的土耳其军射箭入城
The vengeful Turks shot an arrow into the castle...

16
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:56,560
散布德古拉阵亡的谣言
carrying false news of Dracula's death.

17
00:02:56,910 --> 00:02:59,570
伊丽莎白信以为真
Elisabeta, believing him dead...

18
00:02:59,810 --> 00:03:02,470
投河自尽
flung herself into the river.

19
00:03:41,350 --> 00:03:43,340
我的王子死了
My prince is dead.

20
00:03:43,950 --> 00:03:46,080
没有他一切都毫无意义
All is lost without him.

21
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:49,090
但愿能在天上重逢
May God unite us in heaven.

22
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:05,630
(她是自尽死的)

23
00:04:06,110 --> 00:04:08,580
(她的灵魂不能升天堂)

24
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,770
(要受天谴)

25
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,780
(这是神的律令)

26
00:04:22,990 --> 00:04:26,450
(这就是我捍卫教会的报偿吗?)

27
00:04:26,530 --> 00:04:27,520
(放肆)

28
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:31,330
(我唾弃上帝)

29
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:35,860
(我将死后复生)

30
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:40,610
(用尽邪恶力量为她复仇)

31
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:01,430
(血是生命泉源)

32
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:06,360
(我将饮血维生)

33
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:42,660
吸血鬼惊情四百年

34
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,410
伦敦,1897年

35
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:57,470
四个世纪后

36
00:05:58,020 --> 00:06:01,890
(卡费斯区精神病院)

37
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:05,750
我都照你的吩咐做了,主人
I've done everything that you asked, master.

38
00:06:07,230 --> 00:06:10,560
一切准备就绪
All the preparations are in order.

39
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:12,330
万事俱全
Everything.

40
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:14,900
我等待你的命令
I await your command.

41
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:16,890
因为
For I know...

42
00:06:18,110 --> 00:06:20,770
当你论功行赏时
that when the rewards are given...

43
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:25,180
你的慷慨会使我受益无穷
I will be one of those who benefits from your generosity.

44
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,850
谢谢
Thank you.

45
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:36,620
伦费发狂了
Gone mad. Renfield is deranged.

46
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:40,520
心智丧失
He's lost his greedy mind, poor chap.

47
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:45,590
替个外国人德古拉伯爵理财
I want you to take over for his foreign client this rather eccentric Count Dracula.

48
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,930
他要在伦敦近郊买房产
- He's buying up property around London. - Of course, sir.

49
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,870
我会转告伯爵,谢谢你的委派
I'll attend to the count. Thank you for your confidence.

50
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,940
这是你的大好良机,哈克
This is a great opportunity for you, Harker.

51
00:06:55,140 --> 00:06:58,200
但你必须立刻前往川索凡尼亚
But you'll have to leave for Transylvania immediately.

52
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:02,080
终生难遇的机会
Opportunities such as this come but once in a lifetime.

53
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:04,180
那当然
Yes, of course, sir.

54
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:09,010
伦费先生在川索凡尼亚怎么了
If I may inquire...what, in fact, happened to Mr. Renfield in Transylvania?

55
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:12,020
没什么
Nothing. Nothing.

56
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:14,250
私人问题
Personal problems.

57
00:07:14,460 --> 00:07:19,600
完成这些交易你在公司的前途无量
Close these transactions...and your future with this firm is assured.

58
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:22,690
是,我会全力以赴
Yes, sir. I will give it my full attention.

59
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:28,940
我们等了那么久
We've waited this long, haven't we?

60
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:31,600
我一回来就结婚
We can be married when I return.

61
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:35,000
好吧
Of course.

62
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:37,020
我会写信的
I'll write.

63
00:07:38,350 --> 00:07:39,680
强纳生
Jonathan.

64
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,790
强纳生,我爱你
Jonathan, I love you.

65
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,520
我爱你,米娜
I love you, Mina.

66
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:21,560
5月25日,布达佩斯
25th May, Budapest.

67
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:24,060
今晨离开布达佩斯
Left Budapest early this morning.

68
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,820
依我看...
The impression I had was that we were leaving the west...

69
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:30,030
我们是往东欧前进(强纳生哈克之日记)
and entering the east.

70
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:33,510
这一带是罗马尼亚最东部
The district I am to enter is in the extreme east of the country...

71
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:38,210
摩达维亚、布卡维纳及川索凡尼亚
just on the borders of three states...Transylvania, Moldavia and Bukovina...

72
00:08:38,350 --> 00:08:40,410
喀尔巴阡山交界处
in the midst of the Carpathian Mountains...

73
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:43,910
欧洲最荒凉无名的一区
one of the wildest and least known portions of Europe.

74
00:08:47,090 --> 00:08:48,680
朋友
"My friend...

75
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:52,250
欢迎到喀尔巴阡山
welcome to the Carpathians.

76
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:55,520
久候大驾多时
I am anxiously expecting you.

77
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:57,930
我的马车
At the Borgo Pass...

78
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,430
将在波戈隘口等你
my carriage will await you and bring you to me.

79
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:06,210
深信你一路顺畅
I trust yourjourney from London has been a happy one...

80
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:09,700
并希望你在我国
and that you will enjoy your stay...

81
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:12,370
身心愉快
in my beautiful land.

82
00:09:13,110 --> 00:09:14,600
你的朋友敬上 
Your friend,

83
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,850
德
D."

84
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:27,950
5月25日,日记
Diary, 25th May.

85
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:31,890
亲爱的强纳生离去近一周(米娜墨瑞之日记)
My Jonathan has been gone almost a week.

86
00:09:32,170 --> 00:09:35,760
我虽因不能立刻成婚感到失望
And although I was disappointed we could not marry before his departure...

87
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,230
仍为他出使重要任务而高兴
I am happy that he got sent on this important assignment.

88
00:09:39,410 --> 00:09:41,900
我渴望他的音讯
I am longing to hear all the news.

89
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:45,180
到外国一定很有趣
It must be so nice to see strange countries.

90
00:09:46,310 --> 00:09:51,710
不知我们能否一同出国游览
I wonder if we... I mean Jonathan and l...shall ever see them together.

91
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:08,470
我们来早了,还没人来
We're early, driver. No one is here.

92
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:12,670
(死人才走的快)

93
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:30,910
城堡远不远?
I say, is the castle far?

94
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,400
欢迎光临寒舍
Welcome to my home.

95
00:12:53,570 --> 00:12:56,000
轻松自在地进来
Enter freely of your own will...

96
00:12:56,170 --> 00:12:58,830
将你的欢乐留下
and leave some of the happiness you bring.

97
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:00,840
德古拉伯爵
Count Dracula?

98
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,940
在下就是
I am...

99
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:05,000
德古拉
Dracula.

100
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:08,740
寒舍蓬壁生辉了,哈克先生
And I bid you welcome, Mr. Harker, to my house.

101
00:13:12,190 --> 00:13:13,350
请进
Come in.

102
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:32,540
请恕我
You will, I trust, excuse me that I...

103
00:13:33,210 --> 00:13:35,370
不能奉陪
do not join you.

104
00:13:38,110 --> 00:13:40,950
我已经吃过了
But I have already dined.

105
00:13:42,050 --> 00:13:44,280
而且我从不喝
And I never drink...

106
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,280
葡萄酒
wine.

107
00:13:54,230 --> 00:13:57,560
你的祖先? 五官很像
An ancestor? I see a resemblance.

108
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:02,540
德古拉的徽记
The Order of the Dracul.

109
00:14:04,470 --> 00:14:05,900
是条龙
The Dragon.

110
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:09,140
古代有个社
An ancient society...

111
00:14:09,980 --> 00:14:12,410
我的祖先宣誓入会
pledging my forefathers...

112
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:17,650
保护教会抵御外侮
to defend their church against all enemies of Christ.

113
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:24,590
结果却和教会
That relationship was not entirely...

114
00:14:26,190 --> 00:14:27,180
闹僵
successful.

115
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:30,130
是吗?
Oh, yes.

116
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:36,870
这不是开玩笑的事
It is no laughing matter.

117
00:14:40,310 --> 00:14:42,970
我们德古家值得骄傲
We Draculs have a right to be proud.

118
00:14:43,980 --> 00:14:46,810
不论阿提拉大帝如何残暴
What devil or witch was ever so great as Attila...

119
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:49,810
我也流着相同的血液
whose blood flows in these veins?

120
00:14:55,220 --> 00:14:56,380
血！
Blood...

121
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:05,560
这年头成宝了
is too precious a thing in these times.

122
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:13,500
杀伐的年代已过去
The warlike days are over.

123
00:15:15,410 --> 00:15:18,240
我家族的光荣战迹
The victories of my great race...

124
00:15:19,680 --> 00:15:22,340
只成为故事
are but a tale to be told.

125
00:15:25,690 --> 00:15:29,090
我是最后一名子嗣
I am the last of my kind.

126
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:34,930
恕我无知,伯爵
I have offended you with my ignorance, Count.

127
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,530
原谅我
Forgive me.

128
00:15:50,380 --> 00:15:56,080
我渴望在伦敦拥挤的街道行走
I do so long to go through the crowded streets...of your mighty London...

129
00:15:56,220 --> 00:16:00,120
混在匆忙的人群中
to be in the midst of the whirl and the rush of humanity...

130
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:03,450
分享它的生命力
to share its life...

131
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:04,960
它的改变
its changes,

132
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:06,560
及死亡
its death.

133
00:16:06,730 --> 00:16:09,560
完成了 伯爵
There. You, Count, are...

134
00:16:12,730 --> 00:16:15,130
你是卡费教堂的所有人
are the owner of Carfax Abbey at Purfleet.

135
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:16,630
恭喜
Congratulations.

136
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:22,040
贵公司对你赞许有加
Your firm writes most highly...of your talents.

137
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,640
他们说你的品味
They say you are a man of good...

138
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,410
很高
taste.

139
00:16:29,580 --> 00:16:32,070
还说你能力不输给
And that you are a worthy substitute...

140
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:34,410
前任...
to your predecessor,

141
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:36,980
伦费先生
Mr. Renfield.

142
00:16:37,220 --> 00:16:38,990
你可以相信我
You may rely on me, Count.

143
00:16:39,930 --> 00:16:41,490
恕我好奇
Forgive my curiosity, but why ten houses...

144
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:45,060
为何十所房子都买在伦敦附近
in such precise locations around London?

145
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:47,630
炒地皮?
Is it to raise the market value?

146
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:53,200
你相信宿命吗
Do you believe in destiny?

147
00:16:56,380 --> 00:16:59,040
时间都可因...
That even the powers of time...

148
00:17:00,010 --> 00:17:01,070
某一...
can be altered for

149
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:04,650
目的而改变?
a single purpose?

150
00:17:13,730 --> 00:17:19,570
找到真爱的人才是...
The luckiest man who walks on this Earth...is the one who finds...

151
00:17:19,570 --> 00:17:21,230
最幸运的人
true love.

152
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,990
你找到米娜了
You found Mina.

153
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:26,830
我以为丢了呢
I thought she was lost.

154
00:17:27,410 --> 00:17:29,840
我回去后就结婚
We're to be married as soon as I return.

155
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:32,510
你结婚了吗 伯爵?
Are you married, Count?

156
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:35,170
先生
Sir...

157
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:36,780
你结婚了吗?
are you married?

158
00:17:38,690 --> 00:17:40,680
结过一次
I was married once.

159
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:43,920
多年以前
Ages ago, it seems.

160
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:46,590
她死了
She died.

161
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,750
真令人难过
I'm very sorry.

162
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:53,030
是她命好
She was fortunate.

163
00:17:55,770 --> 00:17:59,030
我一生凄凉
My life, at its best, is misery.

164
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:06,870
她一定会是个贤妻
She will no doubt make a devoted wife.

165
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:11,110
而你是个忠实的丈夫
And you a faithful husband.

166
00:18:14,490 --> 00:18:15,480
来
Come.

167
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:18,990
写信给你公司
Write now, my friend, to your firm...

168
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:23,560
与心爱的人,说你要...
and to any loved ones, and say that it shall please you...

169
00:18:24,030 --> 00:18:28,060
陪我住一个月
to stay with me...until a month from now.

170
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,000
一个月?
A month?

171
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:34,430
你要我待那么久?
Do you wish me to stay so long?

172
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:39,680
不可以拒绝
I will take no refusal.

173
00:18:52,630 --> 00:18:55,290
1897年5月3O日,日记
Diary, 30th of May, 1897.

174
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:59,820
强纳生不愿我在他出差时与露西同住
I know that Jonathan does not want me to stay here with Lucy while he is away.

175
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:05,130
他怕我习惯威斯丁家的富贵后
He thinks that if I become accustomed to the wealth of the Westenra family...

176
00:19:05,470 --> 00:19:09,310
便不肯当法律事务所职员的妻子
I will not be content as the wife of a mere clerk in a law firm.

177
00:19:09,540 --> 00:19:12,380
但我和露西自幼是好友
But Lucy and I have been friends since we were children...

178
00:19:12,550 --> 00:19:15,880
她不在乎我只是个教师
and she has never minded that I am only a schoolmistress.

179
00:19:24,890 --> 00:19:26,830
好恶心
How disgustingly awful.

180
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:31,020
米娜
Mina!

181
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:32,460
(一千零一夜)

182
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:34,160
米娜
Mina!

183
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:40,160
米娜,你老在工作
Oh, Mina, you're always working.

184
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:46,240
你那有野心的强纳生逼你学打字?
Is your ambitious Jon Harker...forcing you to learn that ridiculous machine?

185
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:49,680
他也能逼你
When he could be forcing you to perform...

186
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:54,080
低级热情演出
unspeakable acts of desperate passion on the parlor floor.

187
00:19:54,190 --> 00:19:58,020
露西,你不该这样说我未婚夫
Lucy, really.You shouldn't talk about my fiance in such a way.

188
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:01,120
婚姻不只是肉体享乐
There's more to marriage than carnal pleasure.

189
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:06,190
喔 米娜  是哦！
Oh, Mina. So I see.

190
00:20:06,370 --> 00:20:08,360
要多的多
Much, much more.

191
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:12,190
那是
That's...

192
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:17,370
这是什么?露西
What is it, Lucy?

193
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:20,210
我看不懂
Because I don't understand it.

194
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:23,140
男女真的...
Can a man and woman really do...

195
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,150
这么做吗?
that?

196
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:27,750
我昨晚就做过
I did, only last night.

197
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:29,120
骗人!你没有
Fibber. You did not.

198
00:20:29,190 --> 00:20:30,850
我有
Yes, I did.

199
00:20:31,990 --> 00:20:33,980
在我的梦里
Well, in my dreams.

200
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:37,490
强纳生有这么棒吧?
Jonathan measures up, doesn't he?

201
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:40,000
你可以告诉我的
You can tell Lucy.

202
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,440
我们只接过吻
We've kissed. That's all.

203
00:20:44,170 --> 00:20:46,660
他觉得娶不起我
He thinks he's too poor to marry me.

204
00:20:47,740 --> 00:20:51,180
更糟的是我到你的华宅看你
And it's all the worse now that I'm here visiting you at Hillingham...

205
00:20:51,410 --> 00:20:52,900
我的富有朋友
my rich friend.

206
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:56,410
却没人向我求过婚
Yes, but not even one marriage proposal.

207
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:59,080
我快满20了
And here I am, almost 20...

208
00:20:59,250 --> 00:21:01,190
是个老处女了
practically a hag.

209
00:21:07,530 --> 00:21:10,020
昆西摩里斯先生到
Mr. Quincey P. Morris.

210
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:13,100
你看
Oh, look.

211
00:21:13,770 --> 00:21:15,360
那是什么人
What is that?

212
00:21:15,540 --> 00:21:16,930
德州人
A Texan.

213
00:21:17,870 --> 00:21:19,930
昆西摩里斯
Quincey P. Morris.

214
00:21:20,610 --> 00:21:22,940
他好年轻稚气
He's so young and fresh...

215
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:25,370
像我胯间的野种马
like a wild stallion between my legs.

216
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:27,380
你真下流
You're positively indecent.

217
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:29,540
我只是知道男人想要什么
I just know what men desire.

218
00:21:30,120 --> 00:21:31,450
看着
Watch.

219
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:33,480
昆西达令
Quincey, darling.

220
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:35,040
露西小姐
Miss Lucy.

221
00:21:35,620 --> 00:21:37,720
你像春雨般清新
Why, you're as fresh as the spring rain.

222
00:21:37,890 --> 00:21:39,380
谢谢
Oh, thank you.

223
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:42,280
昆西
Quincey.

224
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:46,030
求求你让我摸摸
Please let me touch it.

225
00:21:47,130 --> 00:21:48,120
好...
It's so...

226
00:21:48,970 --> 00:21:50,230
大
big.

227
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:54,640
小女孩
Little girl.

228
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:57,740
我亲爱的小女孩
Oh, my dear, sweet little girl.

229
00:21:58,150 --> 00:22:01,080
我握着你的手,你也吻过我
I hold your hand...- and you've kissed me.

230
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,240
杰克
Jack!

231
00:22:04,150 --> 00:22:06,140
爱你深似海
Oceans of love... Oh, Jack, my darling.

232
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:09,480
我的达令,小宝贝
Poor little baby.

233
00:22:10,090 --> 00:22:11,490
小猫咪过来
My kitten, come over here.

234
00:22:12,090 --> 00:22:13,820
来,吻一个就会好了
Come over here and I'll kiss it better.

235
00:22:14,430 --> 00:22:16,260
我可怜的小花
My poor little blossom.

236
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:19,590
我可怜的小郎中,小医生
My poor little doctor. Brilliant doctor.

237
00:22:19,630 --> 00:22:21,170
嗨 昆西   杰克
- Hello, Quincey. - Jack.

238
00:22:21,170 --> 00:22:23,400
坏熊,我摸摸爪子
What a naughty bear. Let me...

239
00:22:23,470 --> 00:22:25,770
阿瑟荷伍先生到
Arthur Holmwood, Esquire.

240
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,200
阿瑟
Arthur!

241
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:29,930
亲爱的
Oh, my darling.

242
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:33,280
你气色真好
Oh, you look wonderful.

243
00:22:33,450 --> 00:22:34,940
抱歉弄坏你的帽子
I'm so sorry about your hat.

244
00:22:35,980 --> 00:22:36,970
好美 这是我的妖女装
- Charming. - It's my snake dress.

245
00:22:37,050 --> 00:22:39,020
真的吗?
Is it really?

246
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:42,110
露西纯洁有德
Lucy is a pure and virtuous girl...

247
00:22:42,290 --> 00:22:45,850
但她言语大胆真叫我震惊
but I admit that her free way of speaking shocks me sometimes.

248
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:51,960
强纳生说贵族都是口无遮拦
Jonathan says it is a defect of the aristocracy...that they say what they please.

249
00:22:51,970 --> 00:22:53,870
但我崇拜露西
The truth is that I admire Lucy,

250
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:56,800
难怪男人爱她
and I'm not surprised that men flock around her.

251
00:22:57,300 --> 00:23:00,140
我希望我像她一样漂亮迷人
I wish I were as pretty and as adored as she.

252
00:23:18,330 --> 00:23:20,660
他是怎样的人?
What manner of man is this?

253
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:23,720
亚伦费,霍汤公司得力干部
R.M. Renfield, successful solicitor...

254
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:29,740
法律俱乐部受人尊敬的会员(西渥医生之语音日记)
in the firm of Hawkins and Thompkins...respected member of the Lord Nugent's Windem Club...

255
00:23:29,740 --> 00:23:33,330
从川索凡尼亚出差回来
returns from business abroad in Transylvania...

256
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:37,400
精神完全崩溃
promptly suffers a complete mental breakdown.

257
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:41,180
他现在嗜血如命
He's now obsessed with some blood lust.

258
00:23:44,950 --> 00:23:46,610
乔治
George.

259
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,020
在这里等一下
Wait here.

260
00:23:57,930 --> 00:24:02,770
吃开胃菜?西渥先生
Would you care for an hors d'oeuvre, Dr. Seward...

261
00:24:02,770 --> 00:24:04,030
还是点心?
or a canape?

262
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,870
不了,谢谢,伦费先生
No, thank you, Mr. Renfield.

263
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:07,530
今晚感觉如何?
How are you feeling tonight?

264
00:24:08,710 --> 00:24:11,270
比你好,单相思医生
Far better than you, my lovesick doctor.

265
00:24:11,580 --> 00:24:14,270
你对我的私生活有兴趣
Is my personal life of interest to you?

266
00:24:14,450 --> 00:24:16,940
对,我对所有人都有兴趣
Of course it is. All life interests me.

267
00:24:17,450 --> 00:24:18,880
你的食物,伦费先生
Your diet, Mr. Renfield, is disgusting.

268
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:20,380
真恶心
Actually,

269
00:24:20,620 --> 00:24:23,380
实际上很营养
they're perfectly nutritious.

270
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:26,890
我所摄取的生命
You see, each life that I ingest...

271
00:24:27,130 --> 00:24:29,290
会带给我生命
gives back life to me.

272
00:24:33,130 --> 00:24:35,120
苍蝇带给你生命?
A fly gives you life?

273
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:37,130
没错
Certainly.

274
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:42,000
叫我吃一般食物
But you might as well ask a man to eat molecules with a pair of chopsticks...

275
00:24:42,080 --> 00:24:44,810
比用筷子夹分子还难
than to interest me in a lesser carnivore.

276
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:48,470
我要为你发明疯子新分类法
I shall have to invent a new classification of lunatic for you.

277
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:53,410
蜘蛛你吃吗?蜘蛛吃苍蝇
What about spiders? Spiders eat the flies.

278
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:57,410
是的,蜘蛛吃苍蝇
Yes, spiders eat them.

279
00:24:57,660 --> 00:24:59,320
麻雀你吃吗?
What about sparrows?

280
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,490
吃！
Oh, yes.

281
00:25:02,230 --> 00:25:03,590
你刚说麻雀吗?
Did you say sparrows?

282
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:05,750
体型大点的
Something larger, perhaps?

283
00:25:06,500 --> 00:25:07,830
对
Oh, yes.

284
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:11,000
小猫
A kitten.

285
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:12,770
求求你
I beg you.

286
00:25:13,170 --> 00:25:14,770
一只...
A little, sleek... a playful kitten.

287
00:25:15,180 --> 00:25:17,510
受教爱玩
Something I can teach. Something I can feed.

288
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:21,670
可喂食的小猫 小猫而已嘛
No one would refuse me a kitten.

289
00:25:21,950 --> 00:25:24,110
成猫好吗
Wouldn't you prefer a cat?

290
00:25:26,450 --> 00:25:27,780
好
Oh, yes.

291
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:29,510
一只大猫
A big cat.

292
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:32,460
我的救赎全靠它了
- My salvation depends upon it! - Your salvation?

293
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:34,060
你的救赎?没错
Yes. I need lives.

294
00:25:34,130 --> 00:25:37,460
我需要生物,好献给主人
I need lives for the master.

295
00:25:37,530 --> 00:25:38,830
什么主人
What master?

296
00:25:41,270 --> 00:25:43,430
主人即将抵达
The master will come...

297
00:25:44,870 --> 00:25:48,270
他答应要让我不朽
and he has promised to make me immortal.

298
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:49,830
用什么方法?
How?

299
00:25:51,410 --> 00:25:53,140
把他拉开！
Get him off!

300
00:25:54,450 --> 00:25:56,540
血便是生命
The blood is the life!

301
00:25:57,950 --> 00:25:59,890
血便是生命
The blood is the life!

302
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:04,060
5月30日,德古拉城堡
30th May, Castle Dracula.

303
00:26:04,290 --> 00:26:08,230
我发现怪异难言的事
I think strange things which I dare not confess to my own soul.

304
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:10,120
伯爵
The count...

305
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:13,790
看米娜照片的神情让我害怕
the way he looked at Mina's picture fills me with dread...

306
00:26:13,970 --> 00:26:17,100
我仿佛置身在谜团中
as if I have a part to play in a story that is not known to me.

307
00:26:41,930 --> 00:26:43,260
我没听到你进来
I didn't hear you come in.

308
00:26:46,830 --> 00:26:49,390
小心割到
Take care how you cut yourself.

309
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:53,340
刀子比你想象的危险
It is more dangerous than you think.

310
00:26:59,780 --> 00:27:04,180
人类虚荣造出的 邪恶东西
A foul bauble of man's vanity.

311
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:06,270
也许你可以
Perhaps you should...

312
00:27:07,190 --> 00:27:08,850
蓄须
grow a beard.

313
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,620
我要你写的信
The letters I requested.

314
00:27:19,870 --> 00:27:21,700
写了吗?
Have you written them?

315
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:39,810
很好
Good.

316
00:27:49,500 --> 00:27:52,330
你若离开这几间房间
Should you leave these rooms...

317
00:27:54,170 --> 00:27:56,570
劝你切勿...
you will not, by any chance...

318
00:27:56,740 --> 00:27:59,570
到堡内其他区域过夜
go to sleep in any other part of the castle.

319
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:03,740
古堡内
It is old...

320
00:28:05,010 --> 00:28:07,670
有许多可怕的回忆
and has many bad memories.

321
00:28:10,020 --> 00:28:11,420
我警告过你了
Be warned.

322
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:13,180
我充份了解
I'm sure I understand.

323
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:24,600
不要相信这种
Do not put your faith in

324
00:28:24,760 --> 00:28:26,200
小玩意
such trinkets of deceit.

325
00:28:27,870 --> 00:28:29,200
我们在
We are in

326
00:28:29,370 --> 00:28:30,700
川索凡尼亚
Transylvania.

327
00:28:30,870 --> 00:28:34,770
而...川索凡尼亚不同于英国
Transylvania is not England.

328
00:28:35,940 --> 00:28:38,600
我们的风俗习惯与你们不同
Our ways are not your ways.

329
00:28:39,210 --> 00:28:40,700
你一定会
And to you...

330
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:44,640
觉得很怪异
there shall be many strange things.

331
00:28:44,980 --> 00:28:47,890
我已经看到许多怪事
I've seen many strange things already.

332
00:28:48,220 --> 00:28:51,550
狼群追逐我穿过蓝色炼狱
Bloody wolves chasing me through some blue inferno!

333
00:28:57,060 --> 00:28:59,220
你听听
Listen to them.

334
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:06,330
夜童的哭号
The children of the night.

335
00:29:08,910 --> 00:29:11,340
多美妙的音乐
What sweet music they make.

336
00:29:12,010 --> 00:29:13,000
音乐
Music?

337
00:29:13,180 --> 00:29:14,670
那群野兽?
Those animals?

338
00:29:48,650 --> 00:29:51,080
我照德古拉的意思写了三封信
I did as Dracula instructed. I wrote three letters.

339
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:56,150
给公司、家人以及心爱的米娜
To the firm, to my family and to my beloved Mina.

340
00:29:56,590 --> 00:29:59,580
我没提及我的恐惧
I said nothing of my fears as he will read them, no doubt.

341
00:30:04,760 --> 00:30:07,260
因为我知道我成了囚犯
I know now that I am a prisoner.

342
00:31:32,890 --> 00:31:34,080
强纳生！
Jonathan.

343
00:31:35,860 --> 00:31:38,190
强纳生,到我身边
Jonathan, come to me.

344
00:31:47,870 --> 00:31:49,200
来
Come.

345
00:32:08,150 --> 00:32:09,710
躺下
Lay down.

346
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:13,160
躺在我怀里
Lay back into my arms.

347
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:24,570
躺下
Lay back, Jonathan.

348
00:34:16,750 --> 00:34:18,180
(你们干嘛)

349
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,310
(冒牌货)

350
00:34:26,390 --> 00:34:28,120
(不准碰他)

351
00:34:28,190 --> 00:34:30,190
(他是我的)

352
00:34:30,730 --> 00:34:32,720
(你从没恋爱过)

353
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:40,530
(有,我能恋爱)

354
00:34:42,680 --> 00:34:46,740
(而且我将再次恋爱)

355
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:57,880
(那我们今晚没血喝了吗?)

356
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,920
(葳荷米娜墨瑞,希灵汉庄园)

357
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:44,730
吾爱米娜：一切均安
"Dearest Mina, all is well here.

358
00:35:45,040 --> 00:35:49,870
伯爵要我住一个月教他英国礼俗
The count has insisted I remain for a month...to tutor him in English custom.

359
00:35:50,310 --> 00:35:53,040
别他无语,只有我爱你
I can say no more, except I love you.

360
00:35:53,750 --> 00:35:56,150
忠实至终的强纳生上
Ever faithful, Jonathan."

361
00:35:59,790 --> 00:36:03,520
这些信让我陷入绝境
The letters I have written have undoubtedly sealed my doom.

362
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:09,120
伯爵的吉普赛人
The count's gypsies...

363
00:36:09,300 --> 00:36:13,530
英勇战士们  效忠这位贵族,死而无惧
fearless warriors who are loyal to the death to whatever nobleman they serve...

364
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:18,390
他们日夜工作
day and night they toil,

365
00:36:18,670 --> 00:36:23,500
将城堡的土装箱
filling boxes with decrepit earth...from the bowels of the castle.

366
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:29,040
运到刚购入的伦敦卡费教堂
They are to be delivered to his newly acquired Carfax Abbey in London.

367
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:34,050
为什么要装土呢?
Why do they fill these boxes with earth?

368
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:42,890
我爱他!我爱他
I love him! I love him!

369
00:36:43,530 --> 00:36:45,220
米娜
Mina.

370
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:48,660
妙不可言,我决定了
It's so wonderful. I've decided.

371
00:36:48,900 --> 00:36:51,500
我爱他,我要嫁他
I love him and I've said yes.

372
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:53,760
总算!你先别说
Finally. Don't tell me.

373
00:36:53,910 --> 00:36:55,900
带大刀的德州人? 不！
The Texan with the big knife? Oh, no.

374
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:58,170
我要嫁第三号
To my dear number three.

375
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,900
阿瑟荷伍爵爷
Lord Arthur Holmwood.

376
00:37:00,080 --> 00:37:02,240
荷伍勋爵夫妇
Lord and Lady Holmwood.

377
00:37:02,420 --> 00:37:05,180
你做伴娘,答应吧
You are to be my maid of honor. Oh, say yes.

378
00:37:05,790 --> 00:37:09,080
怎么回事?今天是我大喜
Mina, what is it? It's the most exciting day of my life.

379
00:37:10,890 --> 00:37:12,220
你好像漠不关心
You don't seem to care.

380
00:37:12,860 --> 00:37:16,120
我只是很担心强纳生
It's just that I'm so terribly worried about Jonathan.

381
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:18,630
来信语气冷淡
This letter I received is so...

382
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:22,390
很不寻常,根本不像他
It's so cold. It's so unnatural. It's not like him at all.

383
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:25,290
别担心
Mina, don't worry.

384
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:54,130
丰饶女神号,船长日志
Captain's log: : The Demeter.

385
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:56,460
1897年6月27日
27thJune, 1897.

386
00:37:59,470 --> 00:38:02,370
我们载了50箱实验用土
We picked up 50 boxes of experimental earth...

387
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:04,480
前往英国伦敦
bound for London, England.

388
00:38:04,810 --> 00:38:09,840
一场莫名风暴来袭
Set sail at noon into a storm...that seemed to come out of nowhere...

389
00:38:09,950 --> 00:38:12,210
将我们推向汪洋
carrying us out to sea.

390
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:35,740
(伦敦动物园)

391
00:38:47,350 --> 00:38:49,080
7月3日
Third ofJuly.

392
00:38:49,190 --> 00:38:51,090
第二名船员失踪
Second mate has gone missing.

393
00:38:51,190 --> 00:38:52,850
接近直布罗陀海峡
Nearing Gibraltar.

394
00:38:52,990 --> 00:38:54,430
风暴持续肆虐
Storm continues.

395
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:56,250
船员非常不安
Crew uneasy.

