00:59:02,410 --> 00:59:03,670
我找不出原因
I cannot trace the cause.

593
00:59:03,810 --> 00:59:05,170
失血?怎么会
Blood loss? How?

594
00:59:14,990 --> 00:59:16,320
把门关上
My God, close the doors!

595
00:59:27,830 --> 00:59:28,990
天啊
My God...

596
00:59:29,270 --> 00:59:31,000
她还是个孩子
she's only a child.

597
00:59:32,870 --> 00:59:34,300
是啊
Ja.

598
00:59:35,670 --> 00:59:37,070
老天！
My God.

599
00:59:38,180 --> 00:59:42,410
不得延误立刻输血,脱掉外套
There's no time to lose. There must be a transfusion at once.Take off your coat.

600
00:59:43,280 --> 00:59:45,610
还会绑止血带吧
Remember how to tie a tourniquet?Or have you forgotten?

601
00:59:45,750 --> 00:59:47,080
你精通输血?
You perfected a procedure?

602
00:59:47,520 --> 00:59:51,690
精通?不,我只会蓝斯坦法
Perfected? No. I've only experimented.Landsteiner's method.

603
00:59:53,520 --> 00:59:55,680
只替动物输过,山羊、绵羊啦
Animals, goats, sheeps.

604
00:59:57,260 --> 01:00:01,160
若血清有溶血现象红血球会破裂
If hemolysis occurs in the blood donor serum...her red blood cells will explode.

605
01:00:01,500 --> 01:00:03,590
她就会死,把管子拿好
She will die. Take this tube.

606
01:00:07,700 --> 01:00:09,670
你们在搞什么
What in God's name is going on up here?

607
01:00:09,870 --> 01:00:11,430
这位是梵海辛教授
This is Professor Van Helsing, Art.

608
01:00:11,610 --> 01:00:12,910
他把露西怎么了
What the hell is he doing to Lucy?

609
01:00:13,010 --> 01:00:14,270
救她的命
He's trying to save her life.

610
01:00:14,380 --> 01:00:15,140
老天！
Good God!

611
01:00:15,210 --> 01:00:16,410
你是她的未婚夫
You're the fiance?

612
01:00:16,480 --> 01:00:17,640
请让开
Please.

613
01:00:18,380 --> 01:00:19,610
请！
Please.

614
01:00:20,520 --> 01:00:25,280
外套脱掉,她生命垂危须输血
Take off your coat. This young lady's very ill. She's dying.She wants blood and blood she must have.

615
01:00:25,860 --> 01:00:27,190
外套脱掉！
Take off your coat.

616
01:00:27,390 --> 01:00:28,950
袖子卷起来
Roll up your sleeve, Art.

617
01:00:30,590 --> 01:00:32,720
老天！快！
- Oh, God. - Quickly, quickly.

618
01:00:32,960 --> 01:00:34,290
卷起来
Roll it up!

619
01:00:34,670 --> 01:00:36,460
可能有点痛
This may hurt a little, Art.

620
01:00:48,150 --> 01:00:52,550
请原谅我  她是我的命,最后一滴血都行
Forgive me. My life is hers. I would give my last drop of blood to save her.

621
01:00:52,750 --> 01:00:53,810
最后一滴?
Your last drop?

622
01:00:54,580 --> 01:00:56,810
谢谢,欢迎你
Thank you.You are very welcome here.

623
01:00:56,990 --> 01:00:58,960
我不要那么多
I don't ask as much as that.

624
01:00:59,060 --> 01:01:00,150
目前还不要
 Not yet.

625
01:01:00,360 --> 01:01:01,690
握住她的手
Hold her hand.

626
01:01:13,970 --> 01:01:18,540
杰克...她输了两人份的血
Jack, that poor creature has had the blood of two men put into her already.

627
01:01:18,710 --> 01:01:22,300
妈呀!她装不了那么多血
Man alive. Her whole body couldn't hold that much blood.

628
01:01:25,320 --> 01:01:26,680
露西的血去哪呢
What took it out?

629
01:01:26,750 --> 01:01:28,780
问的好,摩里斯先生
That's a good question, Mr. Morris.

630
01:01:34,060 --> 01:01:35,990
喉咙那些痕迹?
Those marks on her throat...

631
01:01:36,230 --> 01:01:40,660
不是疾病或伤痕,而是失血处
no disease, no trituration...I am sure the blood loss occurred there.

632
01:01:41,060 --> 01:01:43,120
血去哪呢?
Oh? Where did the blood go?

633
01:01:44,130 --> 01:01:46,570
你以前是个细心的学生
You were once a careful student, Jack.

634
01:01:46,800 --> 01:01:48,740
用脑呀,血去哪了?告诉我!
Use your brain! Where did the blood go?Tell me!

635
01:01:51,070 --> 01:01:53,470
床铺上有血   没错
- The bed would be covered in blood. - Exactly.

636
01:01:53,810 --> 01:01:58,470
你没观察到不可知的现象
You do not let your eyes see nor your ears hear...that which you cannot account for.

637
01:01:58,650 --> 01:02:02,640
有异物吸她的血后飞走?
Something just went up there, sucked it out of her and flew away?

638
01:02:04,350 --> 01:02:05,910
对 有何不可?
Ja. Why not?

639
01:02:07,020 --> 01:02:10,360
高明,真高明
That's brilliant. That's absolutely brilliant.

640
01:02:10,690 --> 01:02:14,690
请问神医,露西是怎么了?
Will one of you learned doctors... or whatever you are...kindly tell me what is going on with my Lucy?

641
01:02:16,170 --> 01:02:18,600
杰克,你是个科学家
Jack, you are a scientist.

642
01:02:19,040 --> 01:02:23,440
宇宙中可有你不明了的事实?
Do you not think there are things in this universe you cannot understand...and which are true...

643
01:02:23,640 --> 01:02:24,970
像是催眠
mesmerism, hypnotism?

644
01:02:25,110 --> 01:02:26,840
你和夏卡已证实了
You and Charcot have proved hypnotism.

645
01:02:27,040 --> 01:02:29,770
实体与灵体
Materialization, astral bodies.

646
01:02:38,460 --> 01:02:39,790
教授?
Professor?

647
01:02:41,960 --> 01:02:43,190
他去哪了
Where did he go?

648
01:02:46,400 --> 01:02:47,290
看到了吧
You see?

649
01:02:48,400 --> 01:02:50,800
我像是个菜乌
I feel like a blundering novice.

650
01:02:51,070 --> 01:02:53,870
我们对抗的不是疾病
Gentlemen, we're not fighting some disease here.

651
01:02:54,740 --> 01:02:59,040
露西小姐的咬痕是妖魔所致
Those marks on your dear Miss Lucy's neck were made...by something unspeakable out there.

652
01:02:59,040 --> 01:03:00,370
已死又未死
Dead, but not dead.

653
01:03:00,710 --> 01:03:03,610
妖魔追猎我们,原因不明
It stalks us for some dread purpose I do not comprehend.

654
01:03:03,880 --> 01:03:06,640
它吸露西的血维持生命
To live, it feeds on Lucy's precious blood.

655
01:03:06,820 --> 01:03:09,310
是个野兽,怪物
It is a beast, a monster.

656
01:03:27,740 --> 01:03:30,900
我和露西是怎么了
What is happening to Lucy and to me?

657
01:03:31,140 --> 01:03:34,130
年幼时我从不烦躁
When I was younger, my feelings were never troubled.

658
01:03:34,380 --> 01:03:36,570
真希望能恢复往日
I wish I were myself again...

659
01:03:36,750 --> 01:03:39,580
那么敏锐,永可依赖的米娜
the sensible Mina I always depended on.

660
01:03:47,160 --> 01:03:48,750
艾伯森酒
Absinthe...

661
01:03:49,330 --> 01:03:52,160
含春药的成份
is the aphrodisiac of the self.

662
01:03:54,060 --> 01:03:55,760
住在酒里的...
The green fairy...

663
01:03:56,330 --> 01:04:00,070
绿仙子
who lives in the absinthe...

664
01:04:01,470 --> 01:04:03,230
要你的灵魂
wants your soul.

665
01:04:06,080 --> 01:04:07,170
但是
But...

666
01:04:08,850 --> 01:04:10,680
你可以放心
you are safe with me.

667
01:04:26,530 --> 01:04:28,290
王子...
Tell me, Prince...

668
01:04:28,970 --> 01:04:31,090
告诉我你家乡的事
tell me of your home.

669
01:04:33,800 --> 01:04:38,110
全世界最美丽的地方
The most beautiful place...in all creation.

670
01:04:38,940 --> 01:04:42,810
一定是
Yes, it must be.

671
01:04:46,550 --> 01:04:48,880
森林
A land beyond a great,

672
01:04:49,050 --> 01:04:50,450
密布
vast forest...

673
01:04:53,120 --> 01:04:56,120
山峦起伏
surrounded by majestic mountains...

674
01:04:57,790 --> 01:04:59,630
葡萄园
lush vineyards...

675
01:05:01,900 --> 01:05:06,070
遍地无处可比拟的
and flowers of such frailty and beauty...

676
01:05:06,400 --> 01:05:08,840
妖艳花朵
as to be found nowhere else.

677
01:05:18,680 --> 01:05:22,680
你说的好像亲眼看过
You've described my home...as if you had seen it firsthand.

678
01:05:27,090 --> 01:05:29,390
或许受你的声调影响
It's your voice, perhaps.

679
01:05:30,160 --> 01:05:32,090
好熟悉
It's so familiar.

680
01:05:34,400 --> 01:05:35,730
仿佛...
It's like...

681
01:05:37,400 --> 01:05:40,600
梦中无法认出的声音
It's like a voice in a dream I cannot place...

682
01:05:43,270 --> 01:05:45,260
在我孤独时
and it comforts me.

683
01:05:46,110 --> 01:05:47,940
安抚我  在你孤独时
- When I am alone. - When you are alone.

684
01:06:10,470 --> 01:06:12,560
王妃呢?
And what of the princess?

685
01:06:19,380 --> 01:06:20,710
王妃?
Princess?

686
01:06:20,910 --> 01:06:23,240
有王子就有王妃
There is always a princess...

687
01:06:25,150 --> 01:06:27,640
穿着白衣裙
with gowns flowing white.

688
01:06:31,250 --> 01:06:34,820
她的脸
And her face.

689
01:06:35,090 --> 01:06:36,390
天啊
Oh, God...

690
01:06:38,260 --> 01:06:39,730
她的脸
her face...

691
01:06:43,930 --> 01:06:45,200
是条河
is a river.

692
01:06:50,740 --> 01:06:52,400
王妃
The princess...

693
01:06:53,410 --> 01:06:57,810
是条....充满伤痛
she's a river filled with tears of sadness...

694
01:06:58,650 --> 01:07:01,240
心碎泪水的河
and heartbreak.

695
01:07:04,720 --> 01:07:06,660
是有过王妃
There was a princess.

696
01:07:10,330 --> 01:07:11,660
伊丽莎白
Elisabeta.

697
01:07:14,760 --> 01:07:18,930
她是全世界最耀眼的女子
She was the most radiant woman...in all the empires of the world.

698
01:07:26,610 --> 01:07:30,050
谣言拆散了她与王子
Man's deceit took her from her ancient prince.

699
01:07:32,120 --> 01:07:33,610
她投入...
She leapt to her death...

700
01:07:34,220 --> 01:07:37,350
你提到的河而死
into the river that you spoke of.

701
01:07:38,690 --> 01:07:42,050
我的 母语...
In my mother's tongue...

702
01:07:43,060 --> 01:07:48,420
那条河叫
it is called...argesh.

703
01:07:50,500 --> 01:07:52,370
王妃河
River princess.

704
01:09:29,030 --> 01:09:30,260
亲爱的女士
Dear Madam.

705
01:09:30,330 --> 01:09:33,460
你的未婚夫在修道院(阿格莎修女8月12日之信)
Your fiance is safe and in the care...

706
01:09:33,540 --> 01:09:35,940
安然无恙
of the good sisters of the Blessed Sacrament.

707
01:09:37,540 --> 01:09:41,640
哈克先生认为你有生命危险
Mr. Harker believes your life is in extreme danger...

708
01:09:41,840 --> 01:09:45,410
他急切希望你到此
and he desires with all urgency that you join him here...

709
01:09:45,580 --> 01:09:48,420
立刻成婚
so that you may immediately be married.

710
01:09:48,650 --> 01:09:50,880
祝福你
Yours with all blessings,

711
01:09:51,020 --> 01:09:52,850
阿格莎修女上
Sister Agatha.

712
01:09:55,530 --> 01:09:57,320
亲爱的王子
My sweet prince.

713
01:09:58,060 --> 01:10:00,430
绝不能让强纳生知道
Jonathan must never know of us.

714
01:10:08,100 --> 01:10:09,770
露西
Lucy!

715
01:10:09,840 --> 01:10:11,430
我是亚拉汉梵海辛
I'm Abraham Van Helsing.

716
01:10:11,670 --> 01:10:13,010
梵海辛博士
Dr. Van Helsing.

717
01:10:13,180 --> 01:10:16,080
你是米娜小姐,露西的好友?
And you're Madam Mina, dear friend to our Lucy, ja?

718
01:10:16,510 --> 01:10:17,600
她怎样了
How is she, doctor?

719
01:10:17,650 --> 01:10:19,440
仍很虚弱
She's still very weak.

720
01:10:19,750 --> 01:10:24,250
她告诉我你担心你爱的强纳生
She tells me of your beloved Jonathan Harker...and your worry for him.

721
01:10:24,620 --> 01:10:27,280
我为所有的年轻爱侣担心
Well, I, too, worry for all young lovers.

722
01:10:31,460 --> 01:10:33,450
生命中有黑暗
There are darknesses in life, my child...

723
01:10:34,030 --> 01:10:35,960
也有光明
and there are lights.

724
01:10:36,130 --> 01:10:38,790
你便是光明,亲爱的米娜
You are one of the lights, dear Mina...

725
01:10:39,040 --> 01:10:41,230
光明中的光明
the light of all light.

726
01:10:46,710 --> 01:10:48,070
去看你的朋友吧
Go now. See your friend.

727
01:11:04,830 --> 01:11:06,290
米娜
Mina.

728
01:11:09,670 --> 01:11:11,660
你不太一样,米娜
You look different,Mina.

729
01:11:12,440 --> 01:11:15,000
脸上发光
You look positively radiant.

730
01:11:15,610 --> 01:11:17,040
有强纳生的消息
You heard from Jonathan.

731
01:11:17,040 --> 01:11:20,360
是吗?  嗯
- Didn't you? - Yes.

732
01:11:21,010 --> 01:11:22,940
他平安无事,露西
He's safe,Lucy.

733
01:11:23,280 --> 01:11:25,680
在罗马尼亚一家修道院
He's in a convent in Romania.

734
01:11:26,180 --> 01:11:29,170
得了严重的脑热病
He's suffering from a violent brain fever.

735
01:11:29,620 --> 01:11:32,750
修女替他写信
The good sisters are caring for him.They wrote to me,

736
01:11:33,020 --> 01:11:35,080
说他需要我
and they say he needs me...

737
01:11:37,930 --> 01:11:39,090
但....我不去
but I won't go.

738
01:11:39,930 --> 01:11:41,430
我不要丢下你
I'm not going to leave you.

739
01:11:41,500 --> 01:11:42,560
米娜
Mina.

740
01:11:43,970 --> 01:11:46,370
你必须去
You've got to go to him...

741
01:11:46,640 --> 01:11:48,190
你要爱他
and you've got to love him...

742
01:11:49,110 --> 01:11:51,700
立刻嫁给他
and marry him right then and there.

743
01:11:53,310 --> 01:11:55,870
这个你收下
And I want you to take this, my sister.

744
01:11:56,550 --> 01:11:58,410
我送你的贺礼
It's my wedding gift to you.

745
01:11:58,550 --> 01:12:00,020
不,露西
No,Lucy.

746
01:12:00,820 --> 01:12:02,910
别担心任性的小露西
Don't worry about spoiled little Lucy.

747
01:12:05,290 --> 01:12:06,980
我会康复的
I'll be all right.

748
01:12:08,560 --> 01:12:10,860
代我向强纳生致爱
Tell Jonathan oceans of love.

749
01:12:26,510 --> 01:12:27,570
杰克 她怎么了?
Jack, how is she?

750
01:12:46,700 --> 01:12:48,720
我受不了大蒜味
This is why I cannot breathe!

751
01:12:48,800 --> 01:12:50,200
露西 这是药
Lucy, it's medicinal.

752
01:12:50,270 --> 01:12:53,830
会助你睡得好
To help you sleep. To dream better dreams.

753
01:12:54,170 --> 01:12:56,900
只是普通大蒜嘛
It's garlic! It's nothing but common garlic!

754
01:12:57,440 --> 01:12:59,170
昆西来看你了
Quincey's here to see you.

755
01:12:59,340 --> 01:13:00,670
拿点白兰地来
Get some brandy.

756
01:13:00,880 --> 01:13:02,040
露西小姐
Now, Miss Lucy,

757
01:13:02,480 --> 01:13:06,350
你好好休息,阿瑟叫我来看你
you just rest easy.Arthur sent me to take care of you.

758
01:13:07,350 --> 01:13:09,510
他说你不快好,我就得
He said if you don't get better quick...

759
01:13:09,690 --> 01:13:12,090
一枪毙了你,像对跛脚马般
I have to put you out of your misery like a lame horse.

760
01:13:15,090 --> 01:13:17,690
你真野蛮
You're such a beast.

761
01:13:20,700 --> 01:13:22,760
吻我好吗?昆西?
Will you kiss me?Quincey?

762
01:13:25,970 --> 01:13:27,370
吻我
Kiss me.

763
01:13:30,610 --> 01:13:31,600
吻我
Kiss me.

764
01:13:35,240 --> 01:13:37,410
老笨蛋
That old coot!

765
01:13:37,650 --> 01:13:39,240
放开我
Get off me!

766
01:13:39,820 --> 01:13:41,580
露西,听我说
Lucy,Listen to me!

767
01:13:41,820 --> 01:13:43,910
睡觉  快睡觉
Sleep, sleep now. Sleep.

768
01:13:46,360 --> 01:13:48,320
睡吧
You're at peace.

769
01:13:48,320 --> 01:13:49,480
你们看
Look. There. There.

770
01:13:56,070 --> 01:13:57,190
吸血鬼
Nosferatu.

771
01:14:02,670 --> 01:14:05,140
(吸血鬼)

772
01:14:11,280 --> 01:14:13,840
此篇讲述野蛮的
"Here occurs the shocking and frightening history...

773
01:14:14,850 --> 01:14:17,840
德古拉王子骇人野史
of the wild, berserk Prince Dracula...

774
01:14:18,020 --> 01:14:20,010
他将人插住
How he impaled people and roasted them...

775
01:14:20,190 --> 01:14:21,850
烤身、煮头
boiled their heads in a kettle...

776
01:14:22,020 --> 01:14:24,360
活生生的剥皮
how he skinned them alive...

777
01:14:24,530 --> 01:14:27,860
凌迟,饮他们的血
and hacked them to pieces and then drank their blood."

778
01:14:32,770 --> 01:14:34,100
德古拉
Dracul.

779
01:14:35,440 --> 01:14:37,700
血便是生命
For blood is the life.

780
01:14:52,460 --> 01:14:54,390
亲爱的王子
"My dearest Prince,

781
01:14:55,060 --> 01:14:56,390
请原谅我
forgive me.

782
01:14:56,790 --> 01:15:00,060
我收到未婚夫自罗马尼亚的信
I have received word from my fiance in Romania.

783
01:15:00,460 --> 01:15:03,730
我要去见他并完婚
I am en route to join him. We are to be married.

784
01:15:05,000 --> 01:15:06,990
永不再见
I will never see you again.

785
01:15:07,600 --> 01:15:08,930
米娜上
Mina."

786
01:15:18,850 --> 01:15:23,980
奇怪,那位怪友好像也跟来了
It is odd, but I feel almost...that my strange friend is with me.

787
01:15:24,090 --> 01:15:26,610
他在我的思绪中
He speaks to me in my thoughts.

788
01:15:26,760 --> 01:15:30,090
与他在一起我最有活力
With him I felt more alive than ever I had.

789
01:15:30,530 --> 01:15:33,020
如今他不在,又将成婚
And now without him, soon to be a bride...

790
01:15:33,200 --> 01:15:35,690
我深感困惑失落
I feel confused and lost.

791
01:15:36,370 --> 01:15:39,530
也许我虽想做好,其实很坏
Perhaps, though I try to be good, I am bad.

792
01:15:40,370 --> 01:15:43,200
或许我是个善变的坏女人
Perhaps I am a bad, inconstant woman.

793
01:16:02,330 --> 01:16:03,720
飓风！
Winds!

794
01:16:04,730 --> 01:16:06,320
飓风！
Winds!

795
01:16:08,360 --> 01:16:11,490
刮大风吧！
Winds!

796
01:16:14,500 --> 01:16:16,060
就是这原因
It is the cause.

797
01:16:16,740 --> 01:16:19,000
就是它
It is the cause of my soul!

798
01:16:19,680 --> 01:16:21,170
天啊!德古拉
It is Dracula...

799
01:16:21,510 --> 01:16:23,070
这个僵尸
the undead...

800
01:16:23,410 --> 01:16:26,280
我一生追击的敌人
the foe I have pursued all my life.

801
01:16:30,690 --> 01:16:32,620
德古拉!
Dracula!

802
01:16:35,190 --> 01:16:37,850
杰克,快有好多事要告诉你
Jack, hurry! I have much to tell you.

803
01:16:40,100 --> 01:16:42,090
小心守候
Guard her well, Mr. Morris.

804
01:16:42,300 --> 01:16:44,360
今晚不得失误
Do not fail here tonight.

805
01:16:44,530 --> 01:16:49,860
我们对抗的是超越凡人的法力
We are dealing with forces beyond all human experience...an enormous power, so guard her well.

806
01:16:50,210 --> 01:16:53,900
若不尽责你的露西将会成女妖
Otherwise your precious Lucy will become a bitch of the devil...

807
01:16:53,980 --> 01:16:55,770
邪恶的魔女
a whore of darkness!

808
01:16:57,850 --> 01:16:59,370
老疯子
You're a sick old buzzard.

809
01:17:01,050 --> 01:17:02,780
听清楚,小子
Hear me out, young man.

810
01:17:02,950 --> 01:17:05,590
露西不是意外所致
Lucy is not a random victim attacked by mere accident.

811
01:17:05,590 --> 01:17:07,250
明白了吗?   不
Do you understand? No.

812
01:17:07,320 --> 01:17:11,320
她自愿受其蛊惑
She is a willing recruit, a breathless, wanton follower.

813
01:17:11,490 --> 01:17:13,890
忠实的门徒
I dare say, a devoted disciple.

814
01:17:14,060 --> 01:17:16,550
她是魔鬼的姘妇
She is the devil's concubine!

815
01:17:18,500 --> 01:17:19,660
懂了吗
Do you understand me?

816
01:17:21,140 --> 01:17:24,700
但我们仍可救回她的魂
Yet, we may still save her precious soul.

817
01:17:25,010 --> 01:17:29,470
但...得先填饱肚子,杰克
But not on an empty stomach.

818
01:17:29,750 --> 01:17:30,730
杰克  是的,先生
- Jack! - Here, sir.

819
01:17:31,680 --> 01:17:34,010
我饿死了,快跟我去吃
I starve. Feed me.

820
01:17:34,920 --> 01:17:36,210
老傻子！
You old coot!

821
01:19:51,310 --> 01:19:54,640
无能的人类跟愚蠢的驱邪物
Your impotent men with their foolish spells...

822
01:19:54,810 --> 01:19:58,370
保护不了你
cannot protect you from my power.

823
01:20:11,190 --> 01:20:13,990
我诅咒你成为僵尸
I condemn you to living death...

824
01:20:14,760 --> 01:20:17,430
永远
to eternal hunger...

825
01:20:18,100 --> 01:20:22,270
嗜饮...鲜血
for living blood.

826
01:21:46,890 --> 01:21:47,880
杰克
Jack!

827
01:21:55,960 --> 01:21:58,160
我知道你深爱她
I know how deeply you loved her.

828
01:21:58,370 --> 01:22:00,100
所以你得相信
That is why you must trust me and believe.

829
01:22:00,170 --> 01:22:02,160
叫我如何相信?
Believe? How can I believe?

830
01:22:02,440 --> 01:22:06,270
你在天黑前带解剖刀来
I want you to bring me, before nightfall, a set of postmortem knives.

831
01:22:06,440 --> 01:22:08,200
解剖?露西
An autopsy? Lucy?

832
01:22:08,380 --> 01:22:12,040
不算,我要割她的头挖她的心
No, not exactly. I just want to cut off her head and take out her heart.

833
01:22:19,820 --> 01:22:22,450
9月17日,日记
Diary, 17th September.

834
01:22:22,720 --> 01:22:24,320
可怜的强纳生
Poor Jonathan.

835
01:22:24,660 --> 01:22:26,460
他仍重病
He's still so ill.

836
01:22:26,660 --> 01:22:29,560
但回到伦敦他很开心
He's cheered by the familiar streets in London.

837
01:22:30,000 --> 01:22:33,990
而我,因露西已死反而难过
For me, now that Lucy is dead, it is a sad homecoming.

838
01:22:35,340 --> 01:22:38,000
仿佛部份的我也已死去
It is as if a part of me is dead too...

839
01:22:38,140 --> 01:22:40,900
除了暗盼
except for the tiny hope that lives in me...

840
01:22:41,080 --> 01:22:43,570
能再见到我的王子
that I will again see my prince.

841
01:22:43,750 --> 01:22:45,240
他在伦敦吗?
Is he here?

842
01:22:46,350 --> 01:22:47,480
我已结婚,
Now that I am married...

843
01:22:47,480 --> 01:22:51,590
才明白对萦绣山中的他
I begin to understand the nature of my feelings for my strange friend...

844
01:22:51,590 --> 01:22:53,920
是怎样的情绪
who is always in my thoughts.

845
01:23:05,170 --> 01:23:07,100
强纳生,怎么了?
Jonathan, what is it?

846
01:23:07,270 --> 01:23:09,170
就是他
It is the man himself.

847
01:23:09,700 --> 01:23:11,430
他变年轻了
Look, he's grown young.

848
01:23:55,280 --> 01:23:56,610
各位
Gentlemen,

849
01:23:57,750 --> 01:23:59,820
非掘露西的墓不可吗?
must we desecrate poor Lucy's grave?

850
01:23:59,820 --> 01:24:01,760
她死得够惨了
She died horribly enough.

851
01:24:04,460 --> 01:24:07,690
若她已死则无碍
If Miss Lucy is dead, then no wrong can be done to her.

852
01:24:07,900 --> 01:24:09,450
若没死
But if she's not dead...

853
01:24:10,470 --> 01:24:12,700
你是说她被活埋?
What are you saying, man? That she's been buried alive?

854
01:24:13,230 --> 01:24:15,860
不,我只是说
No. All I say is

855
01:24:16,300 --> 01:24:17,790
她没死
she is undead.

856
01:24:18,970 --> 01:24:20,130
没死
Undead.

857
01:24:20,480 --> 01:24:22,030
这真疯狂
This is insane.

858
01:24:41,400 --> 01:24:43,620
各位 动手吧
Gentlemen, shall we?

859
01:24:43,830 --> 01:24:46,230
一、二、三
One, two, three.

860
01:25:03,590 --> 01:25:04,920
她呢?
Where is she?

861
01:25:06,920 --> 01:25:08,410
她呢?
Where is she?

862
01:25:09,760 --> 01:25:11,090
你把她怎么了
What have you done with her?

863
01:25:12,760 --> 01:25:17,430
她住在上帝恩典不及之处飘荡在黑暗界
She lives beyond the grace of God...a wanderer in the outer darkness.

864
01:25:17,430 --> 01:25:20,230
她是吸血鬼
She is vampyre, nosferatu.

865
01:25:21,340 --> 01:25:26,100
这些怪物被吸血后不会死
These creatures do not die like the bee after the first sting...

866
01:25:26,270 --> 01:25:29,270
反受传染而成不朽
but instead grow strong and become immortal...once infected by another nosferatu.

867
01:25:34,780 --> 01:25:36,340
所以,吾友
So my friends,

868
01:25:36,520 --> 01:25:38,780
我们不是对抗一个怪物
we fight not one beast...

869
01:25:38,850 --> 01:25:43,850
而是长久流传以血为生的族群
but legions that go on age after age after age...feeding on the blood of the living.

870
01:25:49,200 --> 01:25:51,460
快躲起来
Quickly, hide. Now.

871
01:26:20,500 --> 01:26:21,960
露西
Lucy!

872
01:26:22,360 --> 01:26:23,090
露西
Lucy!

873
01:26:28,900 --> 01:26:31,000
来,阿瑟
Come to me, Arthur.

874
01:26:32,440 --> 01:26:35,340
扔下其它人,来我这里
Leave these others and come to me.

875
01:26:37,350 --> 01:26:40,280
我好想拥抱你
My arms are hungry for you, my darling.

876
01:26:41,420 --> 01:26:44,080
吻我,抱我
Kiss me and caress me...

877
01:26:44,390 --> 01:26:46,580
我亲爱的丈夫,我求你
my darling husband, please.

878
01:26:46,820 --> 01:26:49,350
我们有十字架和圣水
We wave Christ and His holy blood!

879
01:26:49,660 --> 01:26:52,180
我们在主内坚强
We are strong in the Lord and

880
01:26:52,360 --> 01:26:55,520
主赋与我们力量
the power of His might!

881
01:26:56,760 --> 01:27:00,360
主赋与我们力量
The power of God is upon us!

882
01:27:00,540 --> 01:27:03,200
主赋与我们力量
The power of God is upon us!

883
01:27:05,010 --> 01:27:07,130
主赋与我们力量
The power of God is upon us!

884
01:27:10,810 --> 01:27:13,370
我将你带至光明
I bring you from shadow into light!

885
01:27:13,880 --> 01:27:18,110
黑暗王子,我将你逐至地狱
I cast you out, the prince of darkness...into hell!

886
01:27:21,160 --> 01:27:23,760
只需片刻勇气,
A moment's courage, and it is done.

887
01:27:23,760 --> 01:27:25,690
左手拿凿子
Take the stake in your left hand...

888
01:27:27,630 --> 01:27:29,560
对准心脏
place the point over the heart.

889
01:27:34,400 --> 01:27:36,630
奉主之名,敲下去
Then in God's name, strike. Do it now!

890
01:27:52,520 --> 01:27:54,080
吃呀,大餐
Eat, feast.

891
01:27:54,590 --> 01:27:57,250
将来你们需要力气
You'll need your strength for the dark days ahead.

892
01:27:57,930 --> 01:27:58,920
米娜
Mina?

893
01:28:00,430 --> 01:28:01,590
博士 嗯?
- Doctor? - Ja?

894
01:28:03,330 --> 01:28:04,820
露西怎么死的？
How did Lucy die?

895
01:28:08,200 --> 01:28:09,290
这个...
Well...

896
01:28:11,110 --> 01:28:12,540
她死前痛苦吗？
Was she in great pain?

897
01:28:12,940 --> 01:28:15,270
是的,我们砍掉她的头
Ja, she was in great pain. Then we cut off her head...

898
01:28:15,610 --> 01:28:18,880
在心脏钉下十字架,她就安息了
and drove a stake through her heart and burned it and then she found peace.

899
01:28:19,010 --> 01:28:22,010
博士  拜托别说了
Doctor! Please.

900
01:28:25,950 --> 01:28:27,290
哈克先生
So, Mr. Harker...

901
01:28:28,120 --> 01:28:31,020
身为你的医生,问你个
I must now ask you, as your doctor...

902
01:28:33,900 --> 01:28:35,390
敏感问题
a sensitive question.

903
01:28:35,560 --> 01:28:39,560
你和那些怪物在一起时
During your infidelity with those creatures...those demonic women...

904
01:28:39,700 --> 01:28:41,950
可曾吃过
did you, for one instant,

905
01:28:41,970 --> 01:28:43,300
她们的血
taste of their blood?

906
01:28:44,840 --> 01:28:45,500
没有
No!

907
01:28:49,780 --> 01:28:50,510
没有?
No?

908
01:28:51,710 --> 01:28:52,700
没有
No!

909
01:28:55,150 --> 01:28:56,280
很好
Good!

910
01:28:56,780 --> 01:29:01,620
那你没染上露西那种病
Then you have not infected your blood with the terrible...disease that destroyed poor Lucy.

911
01:29:10,400 --> 01:29:12,660
博士,你要知道
Doctor, you must understand.

912
01:29:14,400 --> 01:29:16,560
以前我疑幻似真
I doubted everything...

913
01:29:16,900 --> 01:29:18,570
甚至以为自己疯了
even my mind.

914
01:29:18,640 --> 01:29:20,800
终日恐惧
I was impotent with fear.

915
01:29:21,310 --> 01:29:22,400
我知道  但是
- I know. - But, sir...

916
01:29:22,580 --> 01:29:27,470
我知道吸血鬼睡在哪
I know where the bastard sleeps.

917
01:29:27,650 --> 01:29:29,310
我把他带到
I brought him there,

918
01:29:29,750 --> 01:29:31,410
卡费教堂
to Carfax Abbey.

919
01:29:34,220 --> 01:29:36,750
吸血鬼的确存在
Vampires do exist.

920
01:29:37,830 --> 01:29:40,820
我们围攻的这一个
And this one we fight, this one we face...

921
01:29:41,100 --> 01:29:43,660
有二十人的力气
has the strength of 20 or more people...

922
01:29:43,830 --> 01:29:45,890
你可以证明
and you can testify for that, Mr. Harker.

923
01:29:46,600 --> 01:29:51,240
他能控制低等的蝙蝠、鼠狼
But he can also control the meaner things of life...the bat, the rodent, the wolf.

924
01:29:51,240 --> 01:29:55,440
可化为烟雾遁形
He can appear as mist, as vapor, as fog and vanish at will.

925
01:29:56,580 --> 01:29:58,510
德古拉法力很大,
Now, all these things Dracula can do...

926
01:29:58,510 --> 01:30:00,180
但他不自由
but he is not free.

927
01:30:00,180 --> 01:30:03,580
他必须躺在故土中增加魔力
He must rest in the sacred earth of his homeland to gain his evil power.

928
01:30:03,750 --> 01:30:06,690
我们必须在此将他毁灭
It is here that we must find him and destroy him utterly.

929
01:30:07,590 --> 01:30:10,850
我替这个伯爵难过
I almost feel pity for anything so hunted as this count.

930
01:30:10,990 --> 01:30:12,980
你怎会怜悯这种怪物
How can you pity such a creature?

931
01:30:14,960 --> 01:30:16,290
我带米娜去我的医院
I'll take Mina to my quarters.

932
01:30:16,700 --> 01:30:18,430
你在那儿才安全
Good. You'll be safer there.

933
01:30:22,000 --> 01:30:25,100
子弹伤不了他,
Mr. Morris, your bullets will not harm him.

934
01:30:25,270 --> 01:30:27,540
一定得砍头 我建议你用猎刀
He must be beheaded. I suggest you use your big bowie knife.

935
01:30:27,710 --> 01:30:30,700
我不打算贴近他,博士
Well, I wasn't plannin' on getting that close, Doc.

936
01:30:31,810 --> 01:30:33,210
主人！
Master!

937
01:30:34,950 --> 01:30:36,380
主人
Master!

938
01:30:37,950 --> 01:30:39,350
主人...
Master!

939
01:30:49,960 --> 01:30:51,730
杰克大夫
Dr. Jack!

940
01:30:52,500 --> 01:30:55,660
我获准得永生
I've been promised eternal life!

941
01:30:57,840 --> 01:30:58,830
杰克
Dr. Seward,

942
01:30:58,910 --> 01:31:00,460
那人是谁
who is that man?

943
01:31:00,640 --> 01:31:03,040
那是伦费先生,你不适合久留
Mr. Renfield. This is no place for you, Madam Mina.

944
01:31:03,240 --> 01:31:06,640
伦费?我得见他
Renfield? I must see him.

945
01:31:07,420 --> 01:31:08,970
伦费先生
Mr. Renfield,

946
01:31:09,420 --> 01:31:10,980
别乱来
behave yourself.

947
01:31:13,320 --> 01:31:15,260
这位是哈克太太
This is Mrs. Harker.

948
01:31:16,990 --> 01:31:18,250
晚安
Good evening.

949
01:31:18,430 --> 01:31:20,330
晚安,伦费先生
Good evening, Mr. Renfield.

950
01:31:20,860 --> 01:31:23,520
我太调皮了
It seems I've been rather naughty.

951
01:31:26,200 --> 01:31:27,530
我认识你
I know you.

952
01:31:28,000 --> 01:31:29,940
你是主人的新娘
You're the bride my master covets.

953
01:31:32,540 --> 01:31:34,770
我有丈夫了
I have a husband.

954
01:31:35,210 --> 01:31:36,870
我是哈克太太
I am Mrs. Harker.

955
01:31:38,210 --> 01:31:40,740
我的主人提过你
My master tells me about you.

956
01:31:42,280 --> 01:31:43,610
他怎么说?
What does he tell you?

957
01:31:44,720 --> 01:31:46,450
说他要来
That he is coming.

958
01:31:47,960 --> 01:31:50,010
他要来找你
That he is coming for you.

959
01:31:50,260 --> 01:31:53,190
过来点
Oh, please.

960
01:31:59,170 --> 01:32:01,190
别留在这
Don't stay here.

961
01:32:01,870 --> 01:32:04,360
离开这些人
Get away from these men,

962
01:32:04,640 --> 01:32:05,970
求求你
please.

963
01:32:07,580 --> 01:32:11,310
我祈求主不要再见到你
And I pray to God I may never see your sweet face again.

964
01:32:15,150 --> 01:32:17,810
愿主祝福保佑你
And may the Lord bless and keep you.

965
01:32:29,260 --> 01:32:30,750
主人！
Master!

966
01:32:31,170 --> 01:32:32,500
主人
Master!

967
01:32:32,930 --> 01:32:35,600
你答应我让我永生的
You promised me eternal life...

968
01:32:36,070 --> 01:32:38,770
你却给了这名美女
but you give it to the pretty woman!

969
01:32:39,270 --> 01:32:40,600
杰克大夫
Dr. Jack!

970
01:32:41,340 --> 01:32:43,330
我不是疯子
I'm no lunatic man!

971
01:32:43,510 --> 01:32:46,410
我很正常,在为灵魂奋战
I'm a sane man fighting for his soul!

972
01:32:46,610 --> 01:32:49,950
我的房间很简陋,但很舒适
My quarters are spare, but I think you will find them comfortable.

973
01:32:50,950 --> 01:32:52,510
杰克大夫
Dr. Jack!

974
01:32:52,790 --> 01:32:55,350
有水和清洁用品
Water and toiletries at your disposal.

975
01:32:57,930 --> 01:33:00,090
你在这十分安全
You'll be completely safe here.

976
01:34:02,320 --> 01:34:03,980
毁掉每个箱子
Destroy every box.

977
01:34:04,160 --> 01:34:06,220
浇圣水
Sterilize the earth inside.

978
01:34:06,430 --> 01:34:07,920
让他无处可逃
Leave him no refuge.

979
01:34:08,500 --> 01:34:10,490
开始驱魔
Let the exorcism begin.

980
01:34:37,290 --> 01:34:38,620
伦费
Renfield.

981
01:34:40,060 --> 01:34:42,720
你背叛了我
You have betrayed me.

982
01:34:44,330 --> 01:34:45,560
没有
No.

983
01:34:47,130 --> 01:34:49,030
主人,我没有
